chili dog with the works,

00:13.026 --> 00:15.761
noticed the suspect checking
for unlocked cars."

00:15.762 --> 00:17.463
It's a police report.

00:17.464 --> 00:19.999
You don't need to tell them
I was getting a chili dog.

00:20.000 --> 00:22.033
What? It's no secret...
look at your shirt.

00:22.936 --> 00:25.371
You're just jealous
I got the collar.

00:25.372 --> 00:26.705
Yeah, y-you got the collar,
y-your tie

00:26.706 --> 00:28.006
and the back of your pants.

00:29.376 --> 00:31.477
Seen triple homicides
with less splatter.

00:31.478 --> 00:35.514
Hey, if your jersey's not dirty,
you didn't play hard.

00:35.515 --> 00:37.083
You want some
more coffee?

00:37.084 --> 00:38.350
That's your third cup.

00:38.351 --> 00:40.085
It tastes good today
for some reason.

00:40.087 --> 00:42.154
Yeah? "Some reason" being
that cute rookie

00:42.155 --> 00:43.722
whose desk is
right by the break area?

00:43.723 --> 00:46.559
I'm a married man, I don't
notice that kind of stuff.

00:46.560 --> 00:48.426
Yeah? You didn't notice
those big beautiful brown eyes?

00:48.428 --> 00:50.896
They're blue.
No further questions, Your Honor.

00:50.897 --> 00:53.631
Got it, one sugar,
three thumbtacks.

00:56.503 --> 00:57.570
You're amazing.

00:57.571 --> 00:59.238
Excuse me?

00:59.239 --> 01:00.573
That's your third
cup of coffee,

01:00.574 --> 01:03.109
and you haven't gone
to the bathroom once.

01:03.110 --> 01:05.111
Eh, that comes from
being out on the beat.

01:05.111 --> 01:07.546
You stop to tinkle,
people could die.

01:07.547 --> 01:09.181
I have so much
to learn.

01:09.182 --> 01:10.416
(chuckles)

01:10.417 --> 01:12.885
Eh, you'll get there, it's
just mind over bladder.

01:12.886 --> 01:15.488
Oh, my God, is that blood
on your shirt?

01:15.489 --> 01:17.490
Well, until the boys
in the lab test it,

01:17.491 --> 01:18.791
we'll never
really know.

01:18.792 --> 01:20.759
But right now all the
evidence points to chili.

01:20.760 --> 01:21.927
Let me get
that for you.

01:21.928 --> 01:23.429
Oh, you don't
have to do that.

01:23.430 --> 01:25.431
I don't mind.

01:25.432 --> 01:27.399
You're a mess.

01:27.400 --> 01:28.868
What are we gonna
do with you?

01:28.869 --> 01:30.401
I don't...

01:32.606 --> 01:35.607
What the hell
did you do?

01:37.077 --> 01:39.078
Are you okay?

01:39.079 --> 01:42.515
Yeah, uh,
just can't sleep.

01:42.516 --> 01:45.350
I told you all that coffee was
gonna get you into trouble.

